snippet.title: CorpoNation: The Sorting Process | Coming to Xbox & Switch!
snippet.description:
CorpoNation is coming to consoles!

The Ringo CorpoNation is here to provide you with everything you need, so after your shift, retire to your Living Pod and compete in pay-to-win games such as Ultimate Ringo Fighters! or, spend some time managing your bills and reading state-approved Ringo News.

All that Ringo asks is that you work hard!... And report any illicit emails or messages to your manager. 

CorpoNation: The Sorting Process is your new dream job. An anti-work, work simulator set in a dystopian world. Coming to Xbox and Switch, May 9!
